<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="G" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Generous" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Generous,</orth> 1) noble, of noble birth: <cit><quote>the g. and gravest citizens,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mm 4.6.13" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. IV, 6, 13</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>most g. sir,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 5.1.96" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 1, 96</bibl></cit>. <emph>of a most select and g. chief in that,</emph> Hml. <bibl n="shak. lll 5.1.3" default="NO" valid="yes">1, 3</bibl>, <bibl n="shak. lll 5.1.3" default="NO" valid="yes">1, 3</bibl> <cit><quote>the g. islanders by you invited,</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 3.3.280" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. III, 3, 280</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) noble-minded, magnanimous, honorable: <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.632" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 632</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 1.5.98" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. I, 5, 98</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 2.2.155" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. II, 2, 155</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 4.7.136" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. IV, 7, 136</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 5.2.253" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 253</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 1.2.8" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. I, 2, 8</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>